  "text": "Threats [CITATION_1] External dangers or conflict with another group Time pressures and faculty availability (either for individual meetings or to serve longitudinally on the committee) are potential threats to group level trust within a competency committee. However, an understaffed committee may lead to higher trust between group members.",
